            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "日本首相高市早苗稱之前談及台灣問題時並未打算提及任何細節",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 日本首相高市早苗表示，在最近遭到中國強烈批評的言論中，她並沒有打算涉及任何有關台灣突發事件的細節。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我並沒有打算提及任何具體細節。」高市周三在國會被問及此事時說道，「僅僅一再重複政府之前的答復，在某些情況下可能會導致預算委員會陷於停滯。國會議員代表的是全體國民，既然被問及具體案例，我便在此背景下真誠作答。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高市也重申了政府的官方立場，即政府將考慮所有可獲得的信息，逐案評估什麼情況對日本構成存亡危機事態。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-0fa9889d-cbbe-3f29-9586-617cab2fbf31-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：川普接連與中、日領導人通話 避免捲入兩國就台灣問題的爭端</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這位首相本月初表示，如果中國攻擊台灣，在某些情況下，日本可能會與其他國家聯合部署兵力。這引發中國政府強烈反應，在外交和經貿方面都採取了行動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Japan’s Takaichi Says Didn’t Intend to Get Specific on Taiwan</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E9%A6%96%E7%9B%B8%E9%AB%98%E5%B8%82%E6%97%A9%E8%8B%97%E7%A8%B1%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D%E8%AB%87%E5%8F%8A%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E6%99%82%E4%B8%A6%E6%9C%AA%E6%89%93%E7%AE%97%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%8A%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E7%B4%B0%E7%AF%80-072554687.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-26 16:10:50",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "乘AI之風扶搖直上 勝宏科技今年已飆升530%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"580\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/C7Gaijdm7BoSI7LCaHYo3w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/fc2eba4ad71cac497ddf814e2ac04b3c\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 今年5月份輝達公司執行長黃仁勳在台灣為供應商舉辦了一場私人宴會。房間裡匯集了全球電子行業的一些頂尖人物，台積電和鴻海的董事長都到場，還有許多當地製造業巨頭。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在為紀念此次盛會而拍攝的集體照中，後排站著一位身穿深色襯衫的男子，可能沒有多少人認識他：陳濤。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他低調的外表下隱藏著日益成長的影響力。這位53歲的前軍人曾在中國的塔克拉瑪干沙漠服役，如今已成為中國最富有的人工智能AI億萬富豪之一——他的財富建立在世界對這項技術永無止境的需求以及與輝達建立的重要合作關係之上。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c9f9f3ec-58c3-3436-b23c-60723ee8d23d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">陳濤是<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:勝宏科技;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/勝宏科技\">勝宏科技</a>(惠州)股份有限公司的創始人，擔任公司董事長。勝宏科技生產印刷電路板(PCB)，這是AI伺服器複雜的電子骨幹。隨著輝達的GPU成為AI革命的發動機，位於中國廣東省惠州市的勝宏科技已成為其核心供應商之一。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">強勁的需求推動勝宏科技股價飆升，使其成為今年MSCI亞太指數中表現最佳的股票，漲幅超過530%。雖然其估值是預期收益的32倍，但這與其他本地晶片製造商100倍以上的估值相比，還相差很遠。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"勝宏科技股價跑贏其他中國熱門股票和美國科技股 \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"580\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/y5EkQupenpyvPOApty.a5w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/30fcff7278fd2fabf21378c44a14a8c2\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">勝宏科技股價跑贏其他中國熱門股票和美國科技股 </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據彭博億萬富豪指數，截至11月25日收盤，陳濤及其妻子劉春蘭的淨資產合計達到91億美元，超越了諸如Pershing Square Capital Management創始人比爾·阿克曼和Blackstone Inc.總裁喬恩·格雷等人。這對夫婦的財富來自他們所持勝宏科技的27%股權。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">陳濤及勝宏科技未回應尋求評論的請求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Couple Rakes in $9 Billion as AI Circuit Board Shares Soar 530%</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Debby Wu.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B9%98ai%E4%B9%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%89%B6%E6%90%96%E7%9B%B4%E4%B8%8A-%E5%8B%9D%E5%AE%8F%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%B7%B2%E9%A3%86%E5%8D%87530-040252388.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-26 12:55:51",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "麥肯錫削減約200個技術崗位 「AI替代」勢不可擋",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 諮詢公司麥肯錫在過去一周削減了約200個全球技術崗位，加入用人工智能(AI)實現部分工作自動化的行業潮流。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據知情人士稱，隨著該公司加大力度採用AI技術，未來兩年不排除在各個職能部門進一步裁員。他們還表示，麥肯錫正在仔細評估哪些任務可以由AI完成。由於細節並未公開，他們不願具名。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「AI為我們和我們的客戶帶來了前所未有的機遇和影響，」一位發言人在電郵聲明中表示。「我們在不斷努力提高專業支持職能的效率和作用，包括利用AI技術。」</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6747fbb3-351c-3665-a1af-1f1e0c21f7f7-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題McKinsey Cuts About 200 Tech Jobs, Shifts More Roles to AI</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%BA%A5%E8%82%AF%E9%8C%AB%E5%89%8A%E6%B8%9B%E7%B4%84200%E5%80%8B%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E5%B4%97%E4%BD%8D-ai%E6%9B%BF%E4%BB%A3-%E5%8B%A2%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E6%93%8B-065812126.html",
