        {
            "title": "花旗聘請前野村和富國銀行交易員 以加強亞洲外匯業務",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"609\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tbVO9MdFlr9Pow1a2kbGDw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwOTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/e83dcd4e69b31e4a6a5b294ec4341b15\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 花旗集團聘請了七名專業人士幫助其加強在亞洲的外匯業務，其中包括野村國際和富國銀行的前交易員。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博看到的該行聲明顯示，曾任職於野村的Nicky Lam已加入花旗的G-10貨幣期權交易團隊。曾在富國銀行和NatWest Markets任職的Jonathan Chua加入了花旗的外匯交易部門，擔任新加坡元交易員。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">花旗的聲明稱，滙豐前全球市場企業銷售主管Manoj Goel已被任命為印度次大陸企業外匯銷售主管。Cassalynne Lou加入了新加坡企業外匯銷售團隊。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-83e8fb04-e54a-35f8-9958-b01f3efb94e6-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"609\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/z5sk4JX5BY.SszBVtI8I5Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwOTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/32d49ed86060121692e6e7fb9fa11293\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Citi Hires Nomura, Wells Traders in FX Business Push Across Asia</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8A%B1%E6%97%97%E8%81%98%E8%AB%8B%E5%89%8D%E9%87%8E%E6%9D%91%E5%92%8C%E5%AF%8C%E5%9C%8B%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%93%A1-%E4%BB%A5%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AF%E6%A5%AD%E5%8B%99-060918515.html",
